---
title: Sesame-Ginger Edamame & Cabbage Rice Salad with Almonds & Crispy Fried Onions
description: This quick, wholesome veggie-forward lunch, makes an ideal light midday meal. It comes together in just 15 minutes and includes a delightful array of textures and flavors that you’ll look forward to all morning! You’ll combine gingery edamame studded jasmine rice with a cabbage-carrot slaw tossed in a bright sesame dressing, then top it with naughty little crispy fried onions and sliced almonds. It’s a crispy, crunchy fresh lunchy you’re going to love.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65aff39ea33a91ae6a3f7e65-a5f0428b.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/65aff39ea33a91ae6a3f7e65.pdf
servings: 2
time required: 15 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/sesame-ginger-edamame-and-cabbage-rice-salad-65aff39ea33a91ae6a3f7e65
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
cuisine: East Asia
nutrition:
  calories: 610 kcal
